{"tid":2196322,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"耿爽: 美國將疫情政治化、污名化、標籤化 最終只會搬起石頭砸自己的腳","createTime":"2020-09-09T21:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T00:59:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"eb88bada520e3cb2fc15aa88c05ea92894ce149e","tid":2196322,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T21:00:18.000Z","msg":"聯合國安理會舉行視像會議，討論有關新型冠狀病毒疫情決議的落實情況。中國常駐聯合國副代表耿爽駁斥美方針對中方在疫情問題上的批評。<br />\n<br />\n美國代表在發言中指責中方抗疫不透明、處置不當，對疫情在全球蔓延負有責任。耿爽當場要求再次發言，作出反駁。他批評美國代表的發言是傳播政治病毒，服務國內政治。耿爽說，今次會議的目的，是討論如何加強國際合作，攜手應對疫情，而不是互相指責、轉嫁責任。中方堅決反對和完全拒絕，美國代表充滿政治惡意和肆意攻擊的發言。<br />\n<br />\n他說，將疫情政治化、污名化、標籤化，諉過於人，挽救不了生命，更不能控制疫情，最終只會搬起石頭砸自己的腳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548787-20200910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548787-20200910.htm&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=77b43dba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548787-20200910.htm&h=057c123d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548787-20200910.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2ac643cf2e0a5dcda3778d1f7a347938eda38be3","tid":2196322,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T21:04:26.000Z","msg":"冬令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ee3a1f11a3da7b8d6bff706416dac6e1831ac8","tid":2196322,"uid":359022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T21:05:08.000Z","msg":"阿爽未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748e829481bbe6eb1b0da1a4281ff4275d5c0e81","tid":2196322,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T21:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又石頭"},{"pid":"6283da685513502fbdc6d426aec5e667beb5d936","tid":2196322,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco